LARDD 1
TITLE PIIX3 IDE Driver Descriptor
TEXT Intel PIIX3 IDE / ATA-PIO descriptor.
SECTION Files
ITEM drv-piix3ide.drfl -> raw DRFL descriptor for PCI 8086:7010.
ITEM piix3ide.rxr -> install bundle containing drv-piix3ide.drfl and driverctl.rxe.
SECTION Install
ITEM rxr verify A:piix3ide.rxr
ITEM rxr install A:piix3ide.rxr
ITEM drivers reload
ITEM drivers
END
